Author: dntlookatmepls
Text: :( Im sorry this is happening to you. That was kinda shitty of your parents to do to you when you expressed vulnerability about your situation. I’m sorry they reacted like that. If you want to talk you can message me

Author: sp00py13
Text: Hi, I just wanted to let you know that I read this, I’m so sorry to hear that you’re struggling, I care about what happens to you, and it sounds like you really need help right now. You’re deserving of it, and there are people out their who know and understand EDs, and they will help you regardless of weight.
